-- AIG Mortgage Insurer Upgraded by S&P on Underwriting, Prices
-- B y   Z a c h a r y   T r a c e r
-- 2013-08-06T15:55:02Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-08-06/aig-mortgage-insurer-upgraded-by-s-p-on-underwriting-prices.html
American International Group Inc.’s
mortgage insurer was upgraded by  Standard & Poor’s , which cited
better underwriting and the higher rates the unit has been
charging for coverage since 2009.  “We believe that operating results will improve,” the
ratings company said today in a statement on New York-based
AIG’s United Guaranty, lifting the rating to BBB+ from BBB.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Zachary Tracer in New York at 
